void OpenSim.Region.Framework.Scenes.SceneObjectPartInventory.ResetInventoryIDs ( bool  ChangeScripts  ) 

Reset UUIDs for all the items in the prim's inventory. This involves either generating new ones or setting existing UUIDs to the correct parent UUIDs.

If this method is called and there are inventory items, then we regard the inventory as having changed.
